{"tid":2053782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友係黃絲 但佢老母搞結婚 幫大陸人落黎香港","createTime":"2020-06-06T14:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T15:59:48.000Z","uid":84295,"like":82,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ecd857493005a22e718b90183755fe48e6d5ebd","tid":2053782,"uid":84295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:44:39.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n我朋友佢係黃絲<br />\n屋企都好多文宣posters<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢出生單親家庭 由細到大同老母關係都好好<br />\n但佢前排同我講<br />\n發現 佢老母竟然一路都有幫<br />\n大陸人搞假結婚黎香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要都係啲 無生產力嘅阿伯<br />\n等佢地黎香港拎公屋 拎福利 睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢話怕老母俾入境處捉<br />\n問我如果有日被入境處捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應唔應該幫佢老母請律師<br />\n各位ching點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評：唔幫 等佢監倉受下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評：幫 始終都係老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d39957fc3d0b3d994dab65195c112f9daa41f7","tid":2053782,"uid":84295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1686f213f8133ee07843005d02ff0737f1a3854","tid":2053782,"uid":84295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"自推x2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e80889886ef2c71f33fe67f711ab76767b6cbd4","tid":2053782,"uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202